+// -*- mode: C++; c-indent-level: 4; c-basic-offset: 4; tab-width: 8 -*-
+//
+// Environment.cpp: Rcpp R/C++ interface class library -- Environments
+//
+// Copyright (C) 2009 - 2010	Romain Francois
+//
